                                    OUT OF OR IN CONNECTION WITH THE SOFTWARE OR THE USE OR OTHER DEALINGS IN THE
                                    SOFTWARE.</strong></p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="license-card">
                                <h3>한국어 요약</h3>
                                <div class="license-summary">
                                    <div class="permission-section">
                                        <h4>✅ 허용사항</h4>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li><strong>상업적 이용</strong> - 상업적 목적으로 사용 가능</li>
                                            <li><strong>수정</strong> - 소스코드를 수정하여 사용 가능</li>
                                            <li><strong>배포</strong> - 소프트웨어를 배포할 수 있음</li>
                                            <li><strong>사적 이용</strong> - 개인적인 용도로 사용 가능</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="condition-section">
                                        <h4>📋 조건사항</h4>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li><strong>라이선스 및 저작권 고지 포함</strong> - 소프트웨어의 모든 사본에 라이선스와 저작권 고지를 포함해야 함</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="limitation-section">
                                        <h4>❌ 제한사항</h4>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li><strong>책임 제한</strong> - 저작자는 소프트웨어와 관련된 어떠한 손해에 대해서도 책임지지 않음</li>
                                            <li><strong>보증 없음</strong> - 소프트웨어는 "있는 그대로" 제공되며 어떠한 보증도 하지 않음</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="license-card">
                                <h3>서드파티 라이선스</h3>
                                <div class="third-party-licenses">
                                    <div class="dependency-item">
                                        <h5>Node.js & npm packages</h5>
                                        <p>다양한 오픈소스 라이브러리를 사용하며, 각각의 라이선스를 준수합니다.</p>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="dependency-item">
                                        <h5>Google Material Symbols</h5>
                                        <p>Apache License 2.0 하에 제공되는 아이콘을 사용합니다.</p>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="dependency-item">
                                        <h5>ONE-Mobile-POP Font</h5>
                                        <p>네이버 클라우드 플랫폼에서 제공하는 무료 폰트를 사용합니다.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="license-card">
                                <h3>소스코드</h3>
                                <div class="source-info">
                                    <p>전체 소스코드는 GitHub에서 확인하실 수 있습니다:</p>
                                    <a href="https://github.com/Tafka-4/MRSPlayground" class="github-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">code</span>
                                        <span>GitHub Repository</span>
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">open_in_new</span>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="license-card">
                                <h3>문의사항</h3>
                                <div class="contact-info">
                                    <p>라이선스와 관련된 문의사항이 있으시면 언제든지 연락해주세요:</p>
                                    <div class="contact-links">
                                        <a href="/contact" class="contact-link">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">mail</span>
                                            <span>문의하기</span>
                                        </a>
                                        <a href="https://github.com/Tafka-4/MRSPlayground/issues" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">bug_report</span>
                                            <span>GitHub Issues</span>
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

        <style>
            .license-section {
                margin-top: 1rem;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 2rem;
            }

            .license-overview {
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }

            .overview-card {
                display: flex;
                gap: 1rem;
                padding: 2rem;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, #667eea 100%);
                border-radius: 1rem;
                color: white;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            }

            [data-theme='dark'] .overview-card {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #667eea 100%);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            }

            .overview-icon {
                flex-shrink: 0;
                width: 64px;
                height: 64px;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
                border-radius: 1rem;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .overview-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .overview-content h3 {
                margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                font-weight: 500;
            }

            .overview-content p {
                margin: 0;
                line-height: 1.6;
                opacity: 0.9;
            }

            .license-content {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .license-card {
                background: var(--card-background);
                border-radius: 1rem;
                padding: 2rem;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
                transition: all 0.2s ease;
            }

            .license-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-2px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }

            [data-theme='dark'] .license-card:hover {
                box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            }

            .license-card h3 {
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-size: 1.3rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
                border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
                padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            }

            .license-text {
                background: var(--background-color);
                border-radius: 0.5rem;
                padding: 1.5rem;
                font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: var(--text-secondary);
                border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color);
            }

            .license-text p {
                margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            }

            .license-text p:last-child {
                margin-bottom: 0;
            }

            .license-summary {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .permission-section h4,
            .condition-section h4,
            .limitation-section h4 {
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            }

            .permission-section h4 {
                color: #48bb78;
            }

            .condition-section h4 {
                color: #4299e1;
            }

            .limitation-section h4 {
                color: #f56565;
            }

            .license-summary ul {
                margin: 0;
                padding-left: 1.25rem;
                color: var(--text-secondary);
            }

            .license-summary li {
                margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }

            .third-party-licenses {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .dependency-item {
                background: var(--background-color);
                border-radius: 0.5rem;
                padding: 1rem;
                border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
            }

            .dependency-item h5 {
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-size: 1rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            }

            .dependency-item p {
                color: var(--text-secondary);
                margin: 0;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }

            .github-link {
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 0.5rem;
                padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
                background: var(--primary-color);
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 0.5rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                transition: all 0.2s ease;
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }

            .github-link:hover {
                background: var(--primary-hover);
                transform: translateY(-1px);
            }

            [data-theme='dark'] .github-link {
                background: #8b5cf6;
                color: white;
            }

            [data-theme='dark'] .github-link:hover {
                background: #7c3aed;
            }

            .contact-links {
                display: flex;
                gap: 1rem;
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }

            .contact-link {
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 0.5rem;
                padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
                background: var(--border-color);
                color: var(--text-primary);
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 0.5rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                transition: all 0.2s ease;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .contact-link:hover {
                background: var(--background-color);
                transform: translateY(-1px);
            }

            @media (max-width: 1024px) {
                .license-summary {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                }
            }

            @media (max-width: 768px) {
                .overview-card {
                    padding: 1.5rem;
                }

                .overview-icon {
                    width: 48px;
                    height: 48px;
                }

                .overview-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
                    font-size: 1.5rem;
                }

                .license-card {
                    padding: 1.5rem;
                }

                .license-text {
                    padding: 1rem;
                    font-size: 0.8rem;
                }

                .contact-links {
                    flex-direction: column;
                    align-items: flex-start;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </body>
</html> 